    • setDefaultFile

      public void setDefaultFile​(java.lang.String name)
      This function allows the file used to populate the dictionary be easily changed. This acts as an iterator even though the json file is not a class, but it defines the IngredientDictionary class and is the basis on which IngredientDictionaries are built. This allows multiple IngredientDictionaries to be iterated through.
      Parameters:
      name - The string directory of the file used to populate the inventory.
